    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this absolute beauty. It's in showroom condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I've taken incredible care of it, and it drives like a dream. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
